        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Dicerapanorpa magna, male genitalia, from Huoditang, Ningshan, Shaanxi. (A), (B) Genital bulb, dorsal and ventral views; (C) genital bulb, ventral view with hypovalves removed; (D, E) aedeagus complex, ventral and caudal views. gcx, gonocoxite; gs, gonostylus; hv, hypovalv; pm, paramere; vv, ventral valve of aedeagus; dv, dorsal valve of aedeagus. Scale bars: A–C = 0.5 mm; D and E = 200 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4608117/files/figure.png" .

